<h2 class="text-center title">上傳簡章規定文件</h2>

<hr>

<div class="alert table-info" role="alert">
    <p>
        致：報名「中華民國僑務委員會 - 海外青年技術訓練班」學生
        <br/><br/>
        請於本頁面上傳招生簡章規定文件，且<strong class="text-danger">紙本報名表件仍須送交至中華民國僑務委員會指定之單位，始完成報名</strong>。
        <br/>
        <small>Please upload the required documents specified in the admission prospectus on this page. <strong class="text-danger">The paper application form must still be submitted to the unit designated by the Overseas Community Affairs Council to complete the application</strong>.</small>
    </p>
    <br/>
    <span class="text-danger">請於<strong class="confirmed-deadline-text">OO月XX日</strong>前，完成以下步驟：</span>
	<ul>
	    <li>
            <span class="text" style="font-weight: bold">步驟&nbsp;①&nbsp;上傳簡章規定文件</span>：
            於本頁面上傳簡章規定之文件後，點選『儲存』按鈕（簡章規定文件詳請見
            <a href="https://ocac-admiss.orbula.net/zh_tw/4year/brochure4" target="_blank">
                《僑委會海青班簡章》
            </a>
            ）。
            <br/>
            <small>
                <strong>Upload documents specified by the prospectus:</strong> After uploading the documents specified in the prospectus on this page, click on the [Save] button (for details of the documents specified in the prospectus, please see the “<a href="https://ocac-admiss.orbula.net/zh_tw/4year/brochure4" target="_blank">Overseas Community Affairs Council -- Overseas Youth Vocational Training Program Application Prospectus</a>”.
            </small>
        </li>

        <li>
            <span class="text" style="font-weight: bold">步驟&nbsp;②&nbsp;線上填報</span>：於本填報系統填寫個人基本資料及選填志願，檢視無誤後點選『確認並鎖定報名基本資料』。
            <br/>
            <small>
                <strong>Online application:</strong> After filling in the basic personal information and preferences in this application system, make sure that the information filled in is correct, and click on “Confirm and secure the basic application information.”
            </small>
        </li>

        <li>
            <span class="text" style="font-weight: bold">步驟&nbsp;③&nbsp;紙本繳件</span>：
            於本填報系統『下載報名表件』頁面列印報名表件，就近送交受理報名單位。
            <br/>
            <small>
                <strong>Paper application:</strong> Print out the application forms on the “Download the Application Form” page of the application system, and submit the forms to the nearest application processing unit.
            </small>
        </li>
	</ul>
</div>

<hr>

<div id="form-uploadArea">
    <div class="card" id="upload-identification-area">
        <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
            僑居地居留證件 <span class="badge badge-danger">必繳</span>
            <br/>
            <small>Residence permit of the country of residence of overseas Chinese <span class="badge badge-danger">Required</span></small>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <div class="alert alert-warning">
                可接受副檔名為 <strong class="text-danger">pdf、jpg、png</strong> 的檔案，單一個檔案大小需 <strong class="text-danger">小於 4 Mbytes</strong> 。
                <br/>
                <small>Files with the extensions <strong class="text-danger">pdf, jpg and png</strong> are accepted, and the size of a single file must be less than <strong class="text-danger">4 Mbytes</strong>.</small>
            </div>

            <div class="row" style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
                <div class="col-12">
                    <input type="file" class="filestyle file-upload" id="identification-upload"
                    data-btnClass="btn-success"
                    data-input="false"
                    data-type="identification"
                    data-text=" 選取檔案"
                    data-Icon="<i class='fa fa-folder-open' aria-hidden='true'/>"
                    multiple>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h4 class="card-title"><span>已上傳檔案</span> <small class="text-muted">(點圖可放大或刪除)</small></h4>
